short_description: socos it is a software development services company based in czechia.
generated_description: socos it, legally known as socos it s.r.o., is a czech company based in prague that specializes in the development of its own software for document management. the company's flagship product, docu-x, includes a document management system (dms) and an optical character recognition (ocr) module for automatic data extraction from corporate documents. socos it's solutions are designed to streamline the processing of electronic and scanned documents, manage iso documentation, handle records and tasks from meetings, manage contract creation and archiving, automate supplier invoice processing, and provide data backup management. the company's software aims to enhance document management efficiency and security for businesses.
